---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Community Organization"
  description="IC&RC Prevention Specialist Domain 4. Coalition-building toolkits, stakeholder-mapping templates, sample MOUs, and event-planning guides."
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="page-header__eyebrow">
        <a href="/professionals">← For prevention professionals</a> · IC&amp;RC PS Domain 4
      </p>
      <h1>Community Organization</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lead">
        Tools to build and sustain the coalitions and partnerships that make
        prevention work at the community level.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>What this domain covers</h2>
      <p>
        Bringing people and organizations together toward shared prevention goals —
        the community-based processes that turn individual efforts into lasting
        change.
      </p>
      <h2>Resources here (filling in)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Coalition-building toolkits</li>
        <li>Stakeholder-mapping templates</li>
        <li>Sample memoranda of understanding (MOUs)</li>
        <li>Event- and meeting-planning guides</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Each state page lists local regulators and organizations that can be
        partners in this work — see <a href="/find-your-state">Find Your State</a>.
        Downloadable toolkits are being added. All resources are free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
